Package comp3111.popnames

Class AnalyzeNames

java.lang.Object
comp3111.popnames.AnalyzeNames
public class AnalyzeNames
extends java.lang.Object
The AnalyzeNames Program implements the methods that are used to calculate the report result. It includes the report functions in tasks 1-3.
